<h1 style="text-align: center;">This is My Homepage!</h1>
<h3>Change Your Homepage.<br></h3>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;">You can change your homepage to any page you want. Just go to <span style="font-weight: bold;">Site </span>-&gt; <span style="font-weight: bold;">Settings&nbsp; </span>and choose a new page from the selection dropdown.<br>
<br></p><h3>Add and Edit Content on Pages</h3>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;">Your pages are composed of "tools" that can be added, edited, and deleted right from within your browser.</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">The text you are reading now was created using the "Text" tool. When in admin mode all tools display a RED toolbar with the tool name to the left, and editing capabilities to the right. <br></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;">Below are examples of common Tools used in +Jade.</p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;">Play around with these samples to familiarize yourself with the tools.</p><p style="margin-left: 40px;">Create new tools on any page by clicking the "Add Content" button located in the topmost Main Admin bar, to the rightmost side.</p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;">Delete tools by clicking the "edit" link within the tool's red toolbar, and clicking "delete". Confirm that you wish to delete the tool, and the tool is instantly removed from your page.
<br></p><p><br></p>